nodes.text: Uggorda was a female Duros who was a member of the Church of the Force. She traveled to the planet Christophsis with four other pilgrims to follow the orders of Brin Izisca and return a crate of kyber crystals back to where they belonged. On the eighth day she was attacked by kyaddak creatures, but she survived. On the tenth day she was killed when a stalactite crushed her head in a cave.
